{"tid":1910919,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法國小玉」往馬桶浴缸狂倒吸水珠　社區水管塞爆…開直播哭腔懺悔","createTime":"2020-03-05T03:58:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T04:35:53.000Z","uid":168698,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9260b7a2789f8981951f05d27ecec1178fcb4ba8","tid":1910919,"uid":168698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:58:24.000Z","msg":"法國一名Youtuber（Cyril）就在影片中示範將一堆吸水珠倒入浴缸跟馬桶、洗手槽內，沒想到最後卻釀成整個社區水管堵塞的悲劇，鄰居家、路旁的排水道內都能看到無法被消化的吸水珠，讓西里爾當場崩潰大哭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4736/d4736596.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4736%2Fd4736596.jpg&h=66306504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n西里爾原本將一堆的彩色吸水珠倒進浴缸，並且試圖進到浴缸泡澡，卻沒想到吸水珠不斷膨脹，最後甚至溢出了浴缸，而西里爾也在馬桶、洗手槽中也倒了吸水珠，導致不斷冒出之外，就連最後把水放掉，部分吸水珠也跟著排進水管造成堵塞。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4736/d4736595.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4736%2Fd4736595.jpg&h=e8bf62e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n西里爾後來試圖想用吸塵器將吸水珠吸出水管，卻未料吸水珠太多、太重，吸塵吸無法負荷而故障。直到他走出戶外才發現，排水孔、鄰居家的水管也冒出自己惡作劇的吸水珠。<br />\n<br />\n當地電視台事後也大篇幅報導，市長很快得知消息後也表示「這是一齣惡作劇，將會逮到惡作劇份子」，西里爾不久也遭到警方詢問，但卻選擇說謊逃避。直到推特上瘋狂轉發他的吸水珠影片，累計超過上千萬次瀏覽，最終西里爾在影片中痛苦表示「自己非常後悔！」並向警方自首。"},{"pid":"79662370cebebf7129d19c3daa9d18850d639044","tid":1910919,"uid":168698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:59:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/ext_tw_video_thumb/1234239927543529474/pu/img/91-bxJO-iLG93ncs?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fext_tw_video_thumb%2F1234239927543529474%2Fpu%2Fimg%2F91-bxJO-iLG93ncs%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=548b3aa5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f3562f993613ce00b265d6fa09d0cc1b3c305ea","tid":1910919,"uid":189528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:03:38.000Z","msg":"一粒一粒吸水珠塞入佢屎眼會點？吸到變木乃衣？"},{"pid":"3c473d42e17168f61058dce486660cf7b7283f0c","tid":1910919,"uid":69841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:05:44.000Z","msg":"香港代表:<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20141028/photo/bkn-20141028125902774-1028_00822_001_01p.jpg?20141028134720\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20141028%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20141028125902774-1028_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20141028134720&h=85d629f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b6591cfb68cd530853da4294d74f7d4a6d067ff","tid":1910919,"uid":65061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:16:17.000Z","msg":"大家絕對唔可以係狗屋做依件事<br />\n好危險 大家唔可以咁做"},{"pid":"eea6828fdb7d312cd6d3c66b0f4d9514226b5441","tid":1910919,"uid":291372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:35:53.000Z","msg":"港鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}